[2025-07-23 01:31:36] [INFO] my_app_logger: Retrieved documents: {'documents': [Document(metadata={'text': None, 'version': 'unknown', 'effective_date': '2025-07-23', 'source': 'Bypassed Safety.pdf', 'page': 0.0, 'doc_id': 'Bypassed Safety'}, page_content='To avoid potential accidents caused by safety devices being mistakenly bypassed.\nAll machines\nAfter each changeover\nMaintenance and Engineering Technicians\n2. BYPASSING SECURITY DEVICES IS STRICTLY \nPROHIBITED. IF THERE IS NO OTHER REMEDY, \nPERMISSION WILL BE ASKED FROM A SUPERIOR \nOFFICER.\n3. When the safety element is bypassed, once the \nsupervisor has been notified and approved, it will \nbe reflected in the "Program Modification" \ndatabase, indicating the machine and the reason \nfor the device bypass. An attempt will be made to \nprevent it from happening again or to find a safer \nway to repair it.\nTOOLS\n1. Occasionally, we find ourselves needing to \nbypass a machine\'s safety device to resolve a \nproblem in its operation and repair it.\nAREA\nCONST2\n5 minutes\nSeguridad Use gloves with mechanical protection.\nUse a safety cap/helmet.\nDo not position yourself under suspended loads.\nVISUAL ASSISTANCE STEP BY STEP\nDOCUMENT TYPE\nSIMPTWW\nPreventive \nMeasures\n- Gloves\n- Safety cap/helmet')]}
[2025-07-23 01:31:36] [INFO] my_app_logger: Retrieved documents: [Document(metadata={'text': None, 'version': 'unknown', 'effective_date': '2025-07-23', 'source': 'Bypassed Safety.pdf', 'page': 0.0, 'doc_id': 'Bypassed Safety'}, page_content='To avoid potential accidents caused by safety devices being mistakenly bypassed.\nAll machines\nAfter each changeover\nMaintenance and Engineering Technicians\n2. BYPASSING SECURITY DEVICES IS STRICTLY \nPROHIBITED. IF THERE IS NO OTHER REMEDY, \nPERMISSION WILL BE ASKED FROM A SUPERIOR \nOFFICER.\n3. When the safety element is bypassed, once the \nsupervisor has been notified and approved, it will \nbe reflected in the "Program Modification" \ndatabase, indicating the machine and the reason \nfor the device bypass. An attempt will be made to \nprevent it from happening again or to find a safer \nway to repair it.\nTOOLS\n1. Occasionally, we find ourselves needing to \nbypass a machine\'s safety device to resolve a \nproblem in its operation and repair it.\nAREA\nCONST2\n5 minutes\nSeguridad Use gloves with mechanical protection.\nUse a safety cap/helmet.\nDo not position yourself under suspended loads.\nVISUAL ASSISTANCE STEP BY STEP\nDOCUMENT TYPE\nSIMPTWW\nPreventive \nMeasures\n- Gloves\n- Safety cap/helmet')]
